Image title

Canadian native, Tom Green, performs a live comedy show for military personnel at Kandahar Air Field, Afghanistan, March 5, 2011. The comedy show is part of the Canadian Army's effort to increase morale and welfare for troops in Kandahar. (U.S. Army photo by Sgt. Canaan Radcliffe/Released)
